[section#expr.alignof
    [:en] Alignof
    [:zh_CN] alignof
]

[para]
[%[`alignof]]
[:en] [%expression[![`alignof]]]
An [`:key alignof] expression yields the alignment requirement of its operand type.
[:zh_CN] [%表达式[![`alignof]]]
[`:key alignof] 表达式生成其操作数类型的对齐要求。

[:en] The operand shall be a [~type-id] representing a complete object type, or
an array thereof, or a reference to one of those types.
[:zh_CN] 其操作数应当为[~类型标识]，表示完整的对象类型或其数组，或表示指代完整的对象类型的引用。

[para]
[:en] The result is a prvalue of type [`std::size_t].
[:zh_CN] 其结果为 [`std::size_t] 类型的纯右值。

[begin:note]
[:en] An [`:key alignof] expression is an integral constant expression ([#expr.const]).
[:zh_CN] [`:key alignof] 表达式是整型常量表达式（[#expr.const]）。

[:en] The [~typedef-name] [`std::size_t] is declared in the standard header
[?libheader cstddef] ([#cstddef.syn], [#support.types.layout]).
[:zh_CN] [~typedef-名] [`std::size_t] 声明于标准头文件 [?libheader cstddef]
（[#cstddef.syn]，[#support.types.layout]）。
[end:note]

[para]
[:en] When [`:key alignof] is applied to a reference type, the result is the
alignment of the referenced type.
[:zh_CN] 当 [`:key alignof] 施加于引用类型时，其结果为被指代的类型的对齐。

[:en] When [`:key alignof] is applied to an array type, the result is the
alignment of the element type.
[:zh_CN] 当 [`:key alignof] 应用于数组类型时，其结果为元素类型的对齐。
